OL,3,CNI finances 'cliff-edge' warning
OL,5,FThe Stormont Executive faces a
OL,6,Ffinancial "cliff-edge" when
OL,7,Fstabilisation funding provided by the
OL,8,FUK Government runs out, MPs have been
OL,9,Ftold.
OL,11,FSir Robert Chote, chairman of the
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland Fiscal Council, said
OL,13,Fthat money which was provided by the
OL,14,FTreasury when the power-sharing
OL,15,FExecutive was restored last year was
OL,16,F"helpful" but would not lead to
OL,17,Ffinancial sustainability for the
OL,18,Fregion.
