OL,5,FA #3.3billion financial package
OL,6,Faccompanied the restoration of
OL,7,Fdevolution in February 2024 following
OL,8,Fa two-year suspension.
OL,10,FThis included a commitment that the
OL,11,Fregion receives 124% of any equivalent
OL,12,Fincrease in funding for England for
OL,13,Fthe policy areas run out of Stormont,
OL,14,Fincluding health, policing and
OL,15,Feducation.
