OL,3,CNI finances 'cliff-edge' warning
OL,5,FThe deal also included a #1.125bn
OL,6,Fstabilisation fund over two years and
OL,7,Fa pledge that a Stormont overspend of
OL,8,F#559million would be written off when
OL,9,Fthe Executive balanced its budget,
OL,10,Fincluding generating #113m in
OL,11,Fadditional revenue.
OL,13,FFinance Minister Caoimhe Archibald
OL,14,Fpublished a Budget Sustainability Plan
OL,15,Fin October that set out details on how
OL,16,Fthe #113mn could be delivered by the
OL,17,Fend of 25/26 financial year.
