OL,3,CNI finances 'cliff-edge' warning
OL,5,FStormont ministers have also since
OL,6,Fagreed a draft budget, but have
OL,7,Fcontinued to warn of huge financial
OL,8,Fchallenges facing their departments.
OL,10,FSir Robert appeared before the
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland Affairs Committee
OL,12,Fhearing on the funding and delivery of
OL,13,Fpublic services in the region.
OL,15,FHe told MPs that the stabilisation
OL,16,Ffunding provided by the Treasury had
OL,17,Fbeen "inescapable" given the financial
OL,18,Fsituation Northern Ireland faced at
OL,19,Fthe time.
OL,26,@yD@FOUyD@RO]
