OL,3,CNI finances 'cliff-edge' warning
OL,5,FHe added: "One challenge at the moment
OL,6,Fis that short-term stabilisation money
OL,7,Fruns out, thus confronting the
OL,8,FExecutive with a potential cliff-edge
OL,9,Fin 2006/2027 when that money goes away
OL,10,Fbut the 24% top-up to the Barnett
OL,11,Fconsequentials won't have been large
OL,12,Fenough to fill that gap.
OL,14,F"I think there is a particular
OL,15,Fchallenge around that point.
OL,26,@mD@KOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
