OL,3,CNI finances 'cliff-edge' warning
OL,5,F"That cliff-edge could in theory move
OL,6,Fforward to 2025/26 if the Executive
OL,7,Fdoesn't manage to balance the budget
OL,8,Fthis year and also to meet its
OL,9,Fcommitment to deliver some #113m of
OL,10,Fadditional revenue as well.
OL,12,F"It (stabilisation funding) has
OL,13,Fclearly helped in the short term but
OL,14,Fdepartments are still over-committed,
OL,15,Fthey are saying they are over-spending
OL,16,Frelative to available funding."
OL,26,@mD@AOUtD@AOUxD@_O]
