OL,3,CNI finances 'cliff-edge' warning
OL,5,FSir Robert said the deficit facing
OL,6,FStormont departments in the current
OL,7,Ffinancial year was now "more
OL,8,Fmanageable" following extra funding
OL,9,Fprovided in Chancellor Rachel Reeves'
OL,10,Fbudget.
OL,12,FHe said: "The short-term stabilisation
OL,13,Fwas certainly helpful but not on its
OL,14,Fown putting you on a sustainable
OL,15,Fpattern for five years ahead."
OL,17,FSir Robert was later asked about the
OL,18,Fpotential benefit of the Executive
OL,19,Fbeing able to set multi-year budgets
OL,20,Fgoing forward.
OL,26,@oD@XOUpD@KO]tD@JOUwD@^O]
