OL,3,CNI finances 'cliff-edge' warning
OL,5,FHe said: "In the Northern Ireland
OL,6,Fcontext this is the 10th or 11th
OL,7,Fconsecutive single year budget, which
OL,8,Fis obviously a different situation
OL,9,Ffrom the (rest of the) UK because for
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland to run a multi-year
OL,11,Fbudget you need to have the
OL,12,Finstitutions to be stable and in place
OL,13,Fand you need to have a multi-year
OL,14,Fbudget at the UK level to give you a
OL,15,Fmulti-year block grant settlement.
OL,17,F"We haven't had that for a decade or
OL,18,Fmore. It is clearly desirable."
OL,26,@mD@JOUyD@AOUzD@_O]
