OL,3,CNI finances 'cliff-edge' warning
OL,5,FNorthern Ireland's comptroller and
OL,6,Fauditor general Dorinnia Carville told
OL,7,Fthe committee that a multi-year budget
OL,8,Fhad to be linked to outcomes from the
OL,9,FExecutive's programme for government.
OL,11,FShe said: "It will allow for longer
OL,12,Fterm planning, especially for large
OL,13,Finfrastructure projects, things that
OL,14,Fnaturally can't be delivered within a
OL,15,Fone-year window.
OL,17,F"The element of certainty and
OL,18,Fstability that would come with that
OL,19,Fshouldn't be overlooked for
OL,20,Fdepartments as well.
OL,26,@sD@KOUyD@AOU
